modName: Bob the Noob Level 200 Follower - DELETED
summary: A level 200 orc follower found in Dead Mans Drink in Falkreath.
descriptionHtml:
Bob the Noob is an expert swordsman and a legendary warrior. He is highly skilled in the art of combat, but secretly Bob loves kittens and fluffy bunnies. 

This mod adds a level 200 orc follower who wears daedric armor and uses a daedric warhammer/Bow. He can be found in dead mans drink in Falkreath and is OVERPOWERED! DO NOT ATTACK HIM! HE IS ESSENTIAL AND WILL KILL YOU! 
Please share any images you have of Bob being awesome!
Cleaned with TES5Edit 

Bugs/Issues: 
None reported so far 

Compatible/Incompatible: 
Must be loaded after Ultimate Follower Overhaul
